name: Arachnid
description:
Real name: Fonzie Hitachi
Throughout the Immortal Wombat series, Arachnid has been a misguided protagonist after his 15th resurrection, following those on the side of chaotic neutral out of curiosity and whimsy over the moving in of his new neighbors; Ted Bundy and Mark Wahlberg. After being restored to his Human form and learning the truth about their deal with Uhaul, he has been a recurring supporting character for the series.
